snippet.title: That "Ghost" Girl in the Woods - Late Night Tales 3
snippet.description:
For your chance to win your own 4x4 Mercedes Sprinter and support a great cause, enter at http://omaze.com/projectamber.

3 years on I revisit the story of the "ghost" girl and delve a little further into that very strange encounter with a bald girl with no shoes, roaming through the French woodland wilderness.


Nukes top 5 video link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MTWk2RSfQ6I&t=2s

Subscribe to keep up with Project.Amber:
https://www.youtube.com/c/projectamber


I've opened an Amazon store! It has all the items I've used to build the van, accessories I have or rate, tools, electrical items, dog bits and much more. This is aimed at answering all of your parts and kit questions:

https://www.amazon.co.uk/shop/projectamber

Updated regularly when I upgrade kit or find better alternatives. Also included is items I get asked about all the time so I've added what I would use if building a camper again.

You can also follow on:
 
Instagram: @project.amber 
http://www.instagram.com/project.amber/

Facebook: 
https://www.facebook.com/ProjectAmber25.Vanlife/

Want to help support the channel?:

Patreon: Project.Amber
https://www.patreon.com/Projectamber

Paypal:
Project.amber25@gmail.com

#Nukestop5 #Omaze #hauntedwoods
